dct_title_s: A map of New Jersey, with part of the adjoining states
dct_description_sm: "Edwd. Yeager, Engraver, Philada." Includes "Table of counties" giving size, population, number of representatives, etc. Includes view of "State Capitol, Trenton." Revision of: A map of the state of New Jersey, with part of the adjoining states / compiled ... by Thomas Gordon. Philadelphia : H.S. Tanner, 1828. A 2nd ed. was issued in 1833.
dct_publisher_sm: Princeton, N.J. : Published and sold by R.E. Hornor, 1850, ©1849.
